Flask-SQLAlchemy extends SQLAlchemy by providing additional integration specifically tailored for Flask applications. It simplifies the setup and configuration of SQLAlchemy within a Flask app, reducing the amount of boilerplate code required to get started.

With flask-sqlalchemy, you can define your database models as Python classes, leveraging SQLAlchemy's ORM capabilities to easily map these classes to database tables.